libplcdocx
==========

A robust Rust framework for placeholder replacement in DOCX files.

libplcdocx provides a flexible and extensible way to process Microsoft Word .docx files by replacing placeholders with dynamic content. It supports custom placeholder syntax, multiple processing modes, XML escaping, file‑size limits, and a hook system for fine‑grained control over the processing pipeline.

  

